title: Cyclic cubic number fields with harmonically balanced capitulation
abstract: It is proved that c = 689347 = 31*37*601 is the smallest conductor of a cyclic cubic number field K whose maximal unramified pro-3-extension E = F(3,infinity,K) possesses an automorphism group G = Gal(E/K) of order 6561 with coinciding relation and generator rank d2(G) = d1(G) = 3 and harmonically balanced transfer kernels kappa(G) in S(13).
comment: 18 pages, 5 tables, 3 figures. arXiv admin note: text overlap with arXiv:2211.11123
